{
  "stem": "12413.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mentioned before about the Black Madonna. it was close to the place-- very close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This was a few hours after the-- the selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I recall you had about 150 escorted by Lithuanians and-- and Latvians, which excelled in [? bestiality. ?] We were order to run.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, this like running one mile uphill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Some were in their 40s.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Some were 35.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Some were sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Some were suffering from asthma.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the Lithuanian and the Latvian were whipping them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was a good runner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was no  problem for me-- my brother to a lesser degree.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Many fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they were shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Then we knew already that they drew a picture of what we are going to face in the future.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the German invaded Czestochowa, for about six, seven months, we are still living in our old places.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We living at the Kopernika Street 20.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it was a normal life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were wearing the armbands with a Star of the David to distinguish us between the Poles and the Jews, because we were living in a mixed-- [INAUDIBLE] community.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I would say in the middle of 1940, then-- maybe the end of 1940, we went to live in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Final Solution started already when we were living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I would say from 19-- end of 1940 to 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "About two years.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
